VALUES ('Emerald and Charcoal Mixed-Media Pop Realism Portrait Prompt', 'A prompt for a stylized portrait using a limited palette of emerald green and charcoal black. It specifies grayscale realism for the subject, who wears sunglasses with emerald reflective lenses and a baroque-designed jacket. The background features dense, overlapping hand-inked patterns, emphasizing bold contrast and glowing emerald accents.', '"Stylised portrait in emerald green and charcoal black palette. Grayscale realism for subject, upward gaze. Sunglasses with muted emerald reflective lenses. Jacket with ornate baroque/filigree black designs, emerald hood underneath. Textured emerald-green fabric draped below. Background: dense, overlapping hand-inked patterns in emerald, charcoal, and subtle silver — radiating lines, geometric shapes, spirals, parallel contour textures, crosshatching, organic waves, dots. Bold contrast, deep blacks, glowing emerald accents. Mixed-media pop realism. Negative prompt: no cartoon, no art style, no painting, no drawings."', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G7o7xmRa4AARvZQ.jpg"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/Beingsayedul/status/1997975120334471537", "sourcePublishedAt": "2025-12-08T10:22:43.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"iamsayedul\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/Beingsayedul\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
