[POST] deconvolution sharpening; chromatic-aberration removal; micro-contrast S-curve; artifact-free edges; grain <3%
[CONSTRAINTS] AR 16:9; forbid stylization, color bleed, softness, fictional anatomy"', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G7nwHTXbsAAASSE.jpg","https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G7nwHTKasAEMBUw.jpg","https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G7nwHS7bYAAYgzl.jpg"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/beginnersblog1/status/1997891927887548895", "sourcePublishedAt": "2025-12-08T04:52:09.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"Beginnersblog\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/beginnersblog1\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
