The man and the neon girl are walking hand-in-hand. Street bokeh lights in the background, shallow depth of field, dramatic lighting, moody cinematic atmosphere, crisp sharp details, full-body shot, realistic shadows on the road, perfect color grading.
Maintain complete accuracy of the man’s face from the reference image — no changes at all.', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G7n0YMZbwAE5baj.jpg"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/MrDasOnX/status/1997896616045633867", "sourcePublishedAt": "2025-12-08T05:10:47.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"Mr Das\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/MrDasOnX\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
