VALUES ('Hygge Winter Family Photo Prompt', 'A detailed prompt for generating a hyperrealistic, cozy winter family photo. It specifies the snowy scene, soft diffused lighting, a neutral color palette with a single accent color, and detailed descriptions of the subjects'' clothing and composition, requiring reference faces to be used without change.', 'Create a realistic high-quality winter family photo using the reference faces without changes. 

