}', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G7kjjXzbQAA9JFi.jpg"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/Taaruk_/status/1997667011439260082", "sourcePublishedAt": "2025-12-07T13:58:25.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"Taaruk\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/Taaruk_\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
