c un • arrière-plan légèrement flou, et des tons chauds et naturels.', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G7VUwYxWMAAh8B9.jpg"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/EloiLJF/status/1996595212345356767", "sourcePublishedAt": "2025-12-04T14:59:28.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"Eloi | UGC IA \ud83e\udde8\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/EloiLJF\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
