VALUES ('Surreal Guy Bourdin Style Pool Scene', 'An evocative image generation prompt in the style of Guy Bourdin, depicting a surreal, high-saturation scene of an empty, crimson-tiled vintage swimming pool at dusk. The scene features overturned furniture and neatly placed sandals, suggesting a mysterious disappearance, with an elongated shadow stretching across the water.', 'In the style of Guy Bourdin.   An empty vintage swimming pool lined with glossy  crimson tiles at dusk. A red metal chair lies  overturned on the wet poolside. A pair of white  heeled sandals placed neatly at the pool''s edge  — as if their owner simply stepped out of existence.  No figure visible.  Only her shadow stretches across the still water,  distorted, elongated, reaching toward something  we cannot see. The sky bleeds deep magenta and  vermillion into the reflection.   High color saturation. Surreal tension.  A narrative frozen mid-sentence.  Something just happened. Or is about to.', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G7ZK6QDW0AAmtAu.jpg"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/dylandddeng/status/1996866080250167327", "sourcePublishedAt": "2025-12-05T08:55:48.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"BubbleBrain\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/dylandddeng\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
