调色风格：怀旧数码相机色调、高对比闪光效果、细腻的屏幕颗粒感、真实的屏幕辉光。', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G7SgEsUbEAA-WXL.jpg"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/ttmouse/status/1996396553741988347", "sourcePublishedAt": "2025-12-04T01:50:04.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"ttmouse\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/ttmouse\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
